name: Laska Shoes
description: The Laska are two-toned dress shoes that deliver both comfort and style. A dynamic diagonal color separation makes the shoes black in front and white in the back and accentuates the slight rise to the heel. An ideal complement to any outfit, Laska shoes also features supremely comfortable padded insoles and can be easily slipped off and on thanks to side zippers.
description_cn: 洛什卡鞋子是双色调的正装鞋，既舒适又时尚。动态的对角线让颜色分离使鞋子前黑后白，突出了鞋跟的轻微上升。作为任何装束的理想搭配，洛什卡鞋子还配备极为舒适的软垫鞋垫，并且借助侧拉链可轻松穿脱。
